OL,3,CPolice urge victims to come forward
OL,4,Cafter MAFS UK rape allegations
OL,6,FThe Department for Culture, Media and
OL,7,FSport says claims of serious sexual
OL,8,Fabuse during filming of Channel Four's
OL,9,F"Married at First Sight UK" are
OL,10,F"serious allegations", as ITV News'
OL,11,FCari Davies reports
OL,13,FPolice have urged any potential
OL,14,Fvictims who were sexually assaulted
OL,15,Fwhile taking part in Married At First
OL,16,FSight UK to get in touch after two
OL,17,Fwomen claimed they were raped during
OL,18,Ftheir time on the show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
