OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779225068
OL,3,CPolice urge victims to come forward
OL,4,Cafter MAFS UK rape allegations
OL,6,FThe two women, who spoke to the BBC
OL,7,Fanonymously, said their onscreen
OL,8,Fhusbands both raped them while the
OL,9,Fshow was being filmed.
OL,11,FAnother woman, Shona Manderson, told
OL,12,Fthe BBC her on-screen partner sexually
OL,13,Fassaulted her.
OL,15,FThe show, which is produced for
OL,16,FChannel 4 by independent production
OL,17,Fcompany CPL, sees single people
OL,18,Fmatched by experts and then "marry",
OL,19,Fwith couples meeting for the first
OL,20,Ftime on their wedding day.
OL,26,@zD@]OUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
