PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779225068
OL,3,CPolice urge victims to come forward
OL,4,Cafter MAFS UK rape allegations
OL,6,FThe "marriages" on the show are not
OL,7,Flegally binding, but the couples go on
OL,8,Fa "honeymoon" and move in together
OL,9,Fafter their weddings.
OL,11,FA Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are aware of media reporting
OL,13,Frelating to allegations of rape and
OL,14,Fsexual assault following the airing of
OL,15,Fa television programme on Monday, May
OL,16,F18.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@OO]pD@COUpD@MO]tD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
