PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779225068
OL,3,CPolice urge victims to come forward
OL,4,Cafter MAFS UK rape allegations
OL,6,F"At this time, we have not received
OL,7,Fany criminal reports in relation to
OL,8,Fthis matter. We will be making
OL,9,Fapproaches to the relevant production
OL,10,Fteams to ensure that anyone they have
OL,11,Fspoken to is aware of how to report
OL,12,Fany criminal allegations to police.
OL,14,F"We continue to encourage anyone who
OL,15,Fbelieves they have been a victim of
OL,16,Fsexual assault, no matter how long ago
OL,17,Fit happened, to get in touch with us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@fO]
