OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779225068
OL,3,CPolice urge victims to come forward
OL,4,Cafter MAFS UK rape allegations
OL,6,FIn a statement to the programme, Ms
OL,7,FManderson's on-screen partner Bradley
OL,8,FSkelly said he categorically denies
OL,9,F"any allegations of sexual misconduct,
OL,10,For that he was controlling".
OL,12,FChannel 4 said in a statement released
OL,13,Fon Monday: "In April, Channel 4 was
OL,14,Fpresented with serious allegations of
OL,15,Fwrongdoing against a small number of
OL,16,Fpast contributors, allegations that we
OL,17,Funderstand those contributors have
OL,18,Fdenied."
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@[O]uD@LOUzD@HO]
