OL,3,CPolice urge victims to come forward
OL,4,Cafter MAFS UK rape allegations
OL,6,FLawyers for CPL, the independent
OL,7,Fproduction company that produces the
OL,8,Fshow, told the BBC its welfare system
OL,9,Ffor MAFS is the "gold standard" and
OL,10,Findustry-leading. They said they acted
OL,11,Fappropriately in all of the cases
OL,12,Fraised by the BBC.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
